{"tid":1240467,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己間歇性缺乏同理心？","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T03:25:28.000Z","uid":12143,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2909d2b380ed9dae969a3b21cac87bae23392b","tid":1240467,"uid":12143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"事件如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如: 好朋友同男朋友嘈交，佢男朋友唔理佢。其實我覺得係自己朋友錯，但佢喊哂口，我都一啲都唔想安慰我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係草率帶過話: 我真係覺得佢好有問題喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如: 有人唔小心打瀉熱綠茶落隻手，我本能反應唔會立刻感覺到佢好痛。只係模仿正常人話 :你有冇事吖？快啲沖水。你要唔要冰吖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如: 有次番工見到有人突發唔知咩病，又暈又屙，病到死死下，而且佢冇咩脈搏。後來無啦啦有生命危險，坐正我對面吊哂鹽水，但我一啲都唔緊張佢會唔會死。<br />\n我以前以為我遇到呢啲事會驚到七彩，點知可以咁鎮定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底咁係冇同理心定 正常人都係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a644d43ddb20e8481e24a3e2175548a44eb2fd2","tid":1240467,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"正常人應該係會指正佢嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4634fdef439412f249ebaa6adf9b862c8232f01","tid":1240467,"uid":12143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a644d43ddb20e8481e24a3e2175548a44eb2fd2","tid":1240467,"uid":59465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"正常人應該係會指正佢嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"I am your user name<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711160b5782f4e8ed5709d1ecd68f360295f46fc","tid":1240467,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4634fdef43941